  <entry>
    <title>node报错</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/01/22/node%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/01/22/node%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99/</id>
    <published>2021-01-22T01:51:57.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-01-22T03:18:18.546Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">(node:28144) Warning: Accessing non-existent property &#39;lineno&#39; of module exports inside circular dependency</span><br><span class="line">(Use &#96;node --trace-warnings ...&#96; to show where the warning was created)</span><br><span class="line">(node:28144) Warning: Accessing non-existent property &#39;column&#39; of module exports inside circular dependency</span><br><span class="line">(node:28144) Warning: Accessing non-existent property &#39;filename&#39; of module exports inside circular dependency</span><br><span class="line">(node:28144) Warning: Accessing non-existent property &#39;lineno&#39; of module exports inside circular dependency</span><br><span class="line">(node:28144) Warning: Accessing non-existent property &#39;column&#39; of module exports inside circular dependency</span><br><span class="line">(node:28144) Warning: Accessing non-existent property &#39;filename&#39; of module exports inside circular dependency</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>当在本地git部署的时候出现这个报错,这个是node的版本太高导致的报错,这个时候就需要更改node的版本在node的<br>官网<a href="https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/releases/">https://nodejs.org/zh-cn/download/releases/</a> 下载以往版本我这里重新用的是12.20.1的node版本</p><p>先要把之前的卸载了然后安装旧版本，在cmd中输入node -v 查看下版本有没有更改</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">C:\Users\82258&gt;node -v</span><br><span class="line">v12.20.1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>这里就更改成功，在git中重新生成就会发现没有node的报错了</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">在搭建博客中遇到node报错的解决方法</summary>
    
    
    
    
    <category term="报错" scheme="http://example.com/tags/%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99/"/>
    
  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>如何实现文件共享vsftp</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2020/11/16/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2020/11/16/%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E5%AE%9E%E7%8E%B0%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6%E5%85%B1%E4%BA%AB/</id>
    <published>2020-11-16T12:12:49.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-01-22T03:18:19.895Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<a id="more"></a><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]# yum -y install vsftpd &#x2F;&#x2F;安装vsftpd插件</span><br><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]# systemctl enable vsftpd  &#x2F;&#x2F;开机自启动</span><br><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]# systemctl start vsftpd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>服务配置<br>实战FTP配置网络YUM源<br>在服务器端部署本地YUM仓库，实现客户端client通过配置FTP服务的服务器的YUM仓库地址实现软件的安装。在服务器端ftp-10修改vsftpd的配置文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@localhost]# cp &#x2F;etc&#x2F;vsftpd&#x2F;vsftpd.conf &#x2F;etc&#x2F;vsftpd&#x2F;vsftpd.conf.bak0</span><br><span class="line">[root@localhost]# vi &#x2F;etc&#x2F;vsftpd&#x2F;vsftpd.conf</span><br><span class="line">在文件里面添加一行配置:anon_root&#x3D;&#x2F;mnt</span><br><span class="line">意思是匿名用户的站点目录</span><br><span class="line">重启服务使配置生效 systemctl restart vsftpd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>在客户端client上更新yum配置文件(在在之前需要将这台虚拟机配置成可以通网)</p><pre><code>将centos.repo里面的文件路径改成[centos]name=centosbaseurl=ftp://192.168.10.128/mnt/   //这个是刚刚配置的ftp服务器enabled=1gpgcheck=0</code></pre><p>client使一个可以访问ftp-10的另外一个系统</p>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">FTP是用来在两台计算机之间传输文件，是Internet中应用非常广泛的服务之一</summary>
    
    
    
    
