  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>数据库主从同步部署</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2020/11/15/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%8E%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A5/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2020/11/15/%E6%95%B0%E6%8D%AE%E5%BA%93%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%BB%E4%BB%8E%E5%90%8C%E6%AD%A5/</id>
    <published>2020-11-15T11:49:24.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-01-08T10:53:00.578Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>一定要关防火墙!!!<br>进行主机解析，让对方能ping通自己<br>在hosts文件中(两台都需要这样改)</p><a id="more"></a><p>mysql1的ip mysql1 mysql1.shenzhi.com<br>mysql2的ip mysql2 mysql2.shenzhi.com<br>可以通过scp传输过去也可以进入另外一个虚拟机中重新写一遍</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scp &#x2F;etc&#x2F;hosts 192.168.220.40:&#x2F;etc  </span><br><span class="line">将这台主机下的&#x2F;etc&#x2F;hosts文件传输到192.168.220.40这台主机下的&#x2F;etc文件夹</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3>主:使用数据库前一定要启动</h3><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">要进行配置离线yum源</span><br><span class="line">yum -y install mariadb mariadb-server  &#x2F;&#x2F;如果没有安装mariadb就安装</span><br><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]# systemctl start mariadb   &#x2F;&#x2F;启动mariadb</span><br><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]# systemctl enable mariadb  &#x2F;&#x2F;永久启动mariadb服务</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4>初始化数据库</h4><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql_secure_installation </span><br><span class="line">初始化的操作和之前的一样</span><br><span class="line">设置密码:000000</span><br><span class="line">关闭远程登陆</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>这个是数据库的配置文件<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]#cp &#x2F;etc&#x2F;my.cnf.d&#x2F;server.cnf &#x2F;etc&#x2F;my.cnf.d&#x2F;server.cnf_bak0</span><br><span class="line">这个是进行备份</span><br><span class="line">[root@localhost ~]# vi &#x2F;etc&#x2F;my.cnf.d&#x2F;server.cnf</span><br><span class="line">[mysqld]</span><br><span class="line">log_bin &#x3D; mysql-bin</span><br><span class="line">binlog_ignore_db &#x3D; mysql&#x2F;&#x2F;这是是vi后找到[mysql]的下一行开始输入log_bin</span><br><span class="line">server_id &#x3D; 30  &#x2F;&#x2F;这里是30可以换成别的数字主要是便于标识</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>通过scp将mysql1的刚刚写的server.cnf复制到mysql2的my.cnf.d文件夹下就可以不用自己打全部内容直接将上面的server_id改成40(也可以不用40这个只是便于标识)<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">scp &#x2F;etc&#x2F;my.cnf.d&#x2F;server.cnf mysql2:&#x2F;etc&#x2F;my.cnf.d</span><br><span class="line">其中直接用mysql2进行传输前一定要主机名解析(&#x2F;etc&#x2F;hosts)</span><br><span class="line">如果没有解析的化是用不了的,也可以直接用对方主机的ip进行传输</span><br><span class="line">[root@mysql2 ~]# vi &#x2F;etc&#x2F;my.cnf.d&#x2F;server.cnf </span><br><span class="line">你会发现你在Mysql1上面配置好的直接到这里了,就直接改server_id就行了</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>主服务器的配置<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql -uroot -p000000  &#x2F;&#x2F;进入数据库</span><br><span class="line">grant all privileges on *.* to &#39;root&#39;@&#39;%&#39; identified by &#39;000000&#39;;</span><br><span class="line">允许任何来的主机通过root来访问(上面有这个命令的解释)</span><br><span class="line">grant replication slave on *.* to &#39;user&#39;@&#39;mysql2&#39; identified by &#39;000000&#39;;</span><br><span class="line">允许从服务器复制 复制的使用使用user用户来登录从mysql2从服务器进行的</span><br><span class="line">slave是从的意思 用user访问mysql2 密码为000000</span><br><span class="line">systemctl restart mariadb  &#x2F;&#x2F;重启mariadb服务建议改完配置或者用之前重启</span><br><span class="line">可以从7-4 23:30看老师总结</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>从服务器的配置初始化数据库<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum -y install mariadb mariadb-server</span><br><span class="line">mysql_secure_installation</span><br><span class="line">初始化的操作和之前的一样</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mysql -uroot -p000000</span><br><span class="line">change master to master_host&#x3D;&#39;mysql1&#39;,master_user&#x3D;&#39;user&#39;,master_password&#x3D;&#39;000000&#39;;</span><br><span class="line">改变master(是主服务器)的角色 master_host是主服务器(mysql1)</span><br><span class="line">访问主服务器的用户是user 访问主服务器的密码是000000</span><br><span class="line">systemctl restart mariadb &#x2F;&#x2F;每次改完数据库一定要重启!!!</span><br><span class="line">mysql -uroot -p000000 &#x2F;&#x2F;再次登陆</span><br><span class="line">start slave; &#x2F;&#x2F;都是在数据库里面输入的一定一定要加;</span><br><span class="line">show slave status\G</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>show slave status\G主要是看这两个地方在主服务器的操作<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">create database test;</span><br><span class="line">show databases;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>在从服务器的操作<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">show databases;可以查看到你在mysql1上面创建的</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;p&gt;一定要关防火墙!!!&lt;br&gt;进行主机解析，让对方能ping通自己&lt;br&gt;在hosts文件中(两台都需要这样改)&lt;/p&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
