  </entry>
  
  <entry>
    <title>nfs服务</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2020/11/13/nfs%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2020/11/13/nfs%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1/</id>
    <published>2020-11-13T03:55:20.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-01-15T14:48:01.539Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>如何实现文件共享nfs</p><a id="more"></a><p>实现在Unix或Linux环境中的文件共享，远程的文件通过共享，可以挂载到本地，就像用本地文件一样<br>nfs如何开展工作？<br>服务器端启动RPC服务<br>服务器端启动NFS服务<br>服务器端向RPC注册端口信息</p><p>客服端启动RPC<br>客户端RPC向服务器端RPC请求NFS服务端口<br>服务器端反馈NFS端口信息给客户端<br>客户端凭借获取的NFS端口访问NFS文件共享<br>安装nfs(记得配置本地的yum源)</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yum -y install nfs-utils</span><br><span class="line">systemctl start rpcbind(在nfs前启动)  </span><br><span class="line">systemctl start nfs-server &#x2F;&#x2F;启动nfs</span><br><span class="line">设置nfs服务自启动</span><br><span class="line">systemctl enable rpcbind</span><br><span class="line">systemctl enable nfs-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>实战1 通过nfs分享yum源给客户端<br>准备<br>nfs服务器：改ip地址    改主机名为nfs-server    进行主机解析<br>nfs客户端：改ip地址    改主机名为nfs-client    进行主机解析<br>这个是在nfs服务器进行配置<br>查看相关软件包是否安装</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">rpm -qa | grep nfs-utils</span><br><span class="line">rpm -qa | grep rpcbind  </span><br><span class="line">如果显示任何东西就是没有安装</span><br><span class="line">安装东西一定要配置离线yum源</span><br><span class="line">yum -y install nfs-utils  &#x2F;&#x2F;安装</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>启动服务</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl start rpcbind</span><br><span class="line">systemctl start nfs-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>查看服务器状态</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl status rpcbind</span><br><span class="line">systemctl status nfs-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>开机自启动</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">systemctl enable rpcbind</span><br><span class="line">systemctl enable nfs-server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>创建分享目录</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir -p &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd  </span><br><span class="line">这里的&#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd可以换成别的目录只不过下面关于&#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd换成你换的那个目录</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>挂在本地光盘到分享目录</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mount &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sr0 &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>修改nfs配置文件</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi &#x2F;etc&#x2F;exports</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd *(rw)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>使服务生效</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">exportfs -r</span><br><span class="line">showmount -e ip &#x2F;&#x2F;就可以看到刚刚在exports输入的东西 ip就是你的服务器的ip</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>客户端测试</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mount &#x2F;dev&#x2F;sr0 &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd  &#x2F;&#x2F;挂载先配置yum源</span><br><span class="line">yum -y install nfs-utils  &#x2F;&#x2F;安装nfs-utils</span><br><span class="line">systemctl start rpcbind  </span><br><span class="line">systemctl start nfs-server</span><br><span class="line">systemctl enable rpcbind  &#x2F;&#x2F;永久启动rpcbind</span><br><span class="line">systemctl enable nfs-server  &#x2F;&#x2F;永久启动nfs-server</span><br><span class="line">systemctl disable firewalld</span><br><span class="line">systemctl stop firewalld &#x2F;&#x2F;关闭防火墙</span><br><span class="line">showmount -e ip  &#x2F;&#x2F;ip为你的nfs服务器的ip  </span><br><span class="line">如果可以看到之前在nfs服务器输入的内容就是成功了</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>进行实验</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mount -t nfs 192.168.220.128:&#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd</span><br><span class="line">-t 是挂载的类型</span><br><span class="line">192.168.220.128  是你的nfs服务器的ip</span><br><span class="line">:&#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd  是使用你nfs服务器的&#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd文件挂载到客户端的&#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd目录下</span><br><span class="line">yum -y install vim   &#x2F;&#x2F;可以进行安装，如果安装成功就是配置成功</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>实战2 共享/share目录，并开放最大nfs共享权限<br>服务器:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir &#x2F;share</span><br><span class="line">vi &#x2F;etc&#x2F;exports &#x2F;&#x2F;在里面输入</span><br><span class="line">&#x2F;share 192.168.220.0&#x2F;24(rw,no_root_squash,no_all_squash,sync,anonuid&#x3D;501,anongih&#x3D;501)</span><br><span class="line">192.168.220.0为你的服务器的网段</span><br><span class="line">exportfs -r  &#x2F;&#x2F;相当于刷新</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>客户端:</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir &#x2F;share  &#x2F;&#x2F;share可以换成别的文件</span><br><span class="line">showmount -e 192.168.220.10</span><br><span class="line">192.168.220.10为你的服务器的ip地址</span><br><span class="line">mount -t nfs 192.168.220.10:&#x2F;share &#x2F;share</span><br><span class="line">永久挂载</span><br><span class="line">echo &#39;192.168.220.10:&#x2F;share &#x2F;share nfs defaults 0 0&#39; &gt;&gt; &#x2F;etc&#x2F;fstab</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>能力升级<br>客户端在挂载的时候遇到的一个问题如下，可能是网络不稳定，NFS默认是用UDP协议，换成TCP协议即可：</p><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mount -t nfs 192.168.220.10:&#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd &#x2F;mnt&#x2F;cd -o proto&#x3D;tcp -o nolock</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
